    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like exhaustion. it feels like the essence of me is just... gone. like the color has been bled out of everything. if there is no art, no creation, no spark... what is actually left? im just a physical object taking up space. is there even a point to staying when the soul of the person is already dead?",
